{"title":"你猜猜","slug":"yougues","date":"2021-01-24T02:04:50.624Z","updated":"2021-01-24T02:24:20.733Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/yougues.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":null,"covers":["https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124100252256.png#pic_center"],"content":"<p><a href=\"https://adworld.xctf.org.cn/task/answer?type=crypto&number=5&grade=1&id=4930&page=1\">你猜猜</a><br>得到txt文件后，发现文本内容为504B开头，猜测为zip文件格式，于是用python将其转化为zip文件后，发<img src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20210124100252256.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\"><br>现可以可以正常打开，内含有flag.txt文件。</p>\n<p>但是需要密码才能打开，暴力破解得到得到密码为123456</p>\n<p>脚本如下</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> struct</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># guess.txt即为输入文件，test.zip即为输出文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">file = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;gess.txt&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;r&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">ss = file.read()</span><br><span class=\"line\">f = <span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test.zip&quot;</span>, <span class=\"string\">&quot;wb&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">i = <span class=\"number\">0</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">while</span> i &lt; <span class=\"built_in\">len</span>(ss):</span><br><span class=\"line\"> s = ss[i:i+<span class=\"number\">2</span>]</span><br><span class=\"line\"> temp = <span class=\"built_in\">int</span>(s, <span class=\"number\">16</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"> f.write(struct.pack(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;B&#x27;</span>, temp))</span><br><span class=\"line\"> i += <span class=\"number\">2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">file.close()</span><br><span class=\"line\">f.close()</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">import</span> zipfile</span><br><span class=\"line\">zFile = zipfile.ZipFile(<span class=\"string\">&quot;test.zip&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">pwdlists=<span class=\"built_in\">open</span>(<span class=\"string\">r&#x27;C:\\Users\\13762\\Desktop\\password.txt&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">for</span> line <span class=\"keyword\">in</span> pwdlists.readlines():</span><br><span class=\"line\">    password=line.strip(<span class=\"string\">&#x27;\\n&#x27;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">#print(1,end=&#x27;&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">try</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">        zFile.extractall(path=<span class=\"string\">&#x27;flag&#x27;</span>,pwd=password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(<span class=\"string\">&quot;password is:&quot;</span>+password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">except</span>:</span><br><span class=\"line\">        print(password)</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">pass</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}